definition: "water" radical in Chinese characters (Kangxi radical 85), occurring in 没, 法, 流 etc/see also 三點水|三点水[san1 dian3 shui3]
surname Ji/abbr. for Jilin Province 吉林省[Ji2 lin2 Sheng3]

sentences.english: Clean and bright, You look happy to meet me.
sentences.chinese: 小而白，洁又亮，见到我你面露喜色。

sentences.english: Jessica owns a house near the coast.
sentences.chinese: 洁西卡在海边有一栋房子。

sentences.english: We are your hosts Mark, along with Wen-Jie.
sentences.chinese: 马可和文洁我在这儿向你问候。

sentences.english: And they shall teach my people the difference between holy and profane, and shew them how to discern between clean and unclean.
sentences.chinese: 他们应教训我的百姓区别圣与俗，知道洁与不洁。

sentences.english: The next semester, Jessica tried again.
sentences.chinese: 在接下来的那个学期，洁西卡再次尝试。

sentences.english: The teacher love classmate, the world be the great, the tallest Jie.
sentences.chinese: 老师对同学的爱，天下最伟大，最高洁。

sentences.english: It was about time that Jessica got rid of that no-good boyfriend!
sentences.chinese: 也该是洁西卡甩掉一无是处的男友的时候了。

sentences.english: Jessica, an old friend of mine, went to a concert over the weekend.
sentences.chinese: 我的老朋友洁西卡上周末去听了一场演唱会。

sentences.english: Diglant SY - D001 with olive design, clean slips through the first luxury.
sentences.chinese: 采用橄榄型设计，洁简中透首奢华。

sentences.english: We are your friends Mark, along with Wen-Jie.
sentences.chinese: 我们是你的广播朋友马可和文洁。

sentences.english: Enjoy teeth-cleaning chews or biscuits and tooth brushing three times per week.
sentences.chinese: 享受牙齿清洁或咀嚼饼干和每周清扫洁牙齿三次。

sentences.english: Jessica and Joyce were best friends in ninth grade.
sentences.chinese: 在九年级时，洁西卡和乔依丝是最好的朋友。

sentences.english: Super-concentrated, Chlorinated special formula for powerful cleaning and Maximum Economy.
sentences.chinese: 超浓缩强力氯化高效配方，洁力特强，经济耐用。

definition: to soar/to glide/variant of 詳|详[xiang2]
surname Lan/abbr. for Lanzhou 蘭州|兰州[Lan2 zhou1], Gansu
orchid (蘭花|兰花 Cymbidium goeringii)/fragrant thoroughwort (蘭草|兰草 Eupatorium fortunei)/lily magnolia (木蘭|木兰)
